@startuml
skinparam style strict

actor Client
participant "Authorization Server" as AS
participant "Resource Server" as RS

== Token Issuance ==

Client -> AS: (A) Token Request\n(DPoP Proof)
note right of AS: The AS verifies the DPoP Proof\nand binds the token to the client's key.

AS --> Client: (B) DPoP-Bound Access Token\n(token_type=DPoP)

== Resource Access ==

Client -> RS: (C) DPoP-Bound Access Token\n(DPoP Proof)
note right of RS: The RS verifies the token signature\nand the DPoP Proof against the token's key.

RS --> Client: (D) Protected Resource

@enduml